    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in solid 'good' condition, having been consistently maintained and cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics function as intended, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It drives smoothly and represents a reliable, honest example of this model for anyone seeking a well-kept used car.",
