    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and bodywork to be roadworthy again. The engine has a noticeable knock, and the transmission is slipping between gears, suggesting a major overhaul is needed soon. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several deep dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functioning electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, making it a potential candidate for a parts car or a dedicated restoration project for someone with the right tools.",
