      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-quality condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior upholstery, has been meticulously maintained to meet the most discerning standards. Mechanical performance is peerless, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unparalleled integrity and aesthetic perfection.",
